cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.SE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) category as it deals with the problem of defining intelligence in machines. It could also be classified under Machine Learning (cs.LG) as it involves formalizing the essential features of human intelligence. Neural Networks (cs.NE) is another possible category as the paper may discuss the use of neural networks in measuring machine intelligence. Robotics (cs.RO) is also a possible category as the paper may discuss the application of machine intelligence in robotics. Finally, Software Engineering (cs.SE) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the development of software systems that exhibit machine intelligence.
